# Jetpack Compose with MVVM: ViewModel and LiveData
[](/@manishkumar_75473?source=post_page---byline--3d175bb0c7b6---------------------------------------)[Manish Kumar](/@manishkumar_75473?source=post_page---byline--3d175bb0c7b6---------------------------------------)Follow3 min readDec 27, 2024[
